      "value": "<p>A ray of sickening greenish energy lashes out toward a creature within range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 2d8 poison damage and must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, it is also poisoned until the end of your next turn.</p><h3>At Higher Levels</h3><p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 1st.</p><p><strong>Spell Lists.</strong> Sorcerer, Wizard</p>",
